descp2: A boolean value indicating whether the NumPy-array semantics should be turned on or off. When this flag is set to True, it enables Gluon code flow to use or generate mxnet.numpy.ndarray`s instead of `mxnet.ndarray.NDArray. For example, a Block would create parameters of type mxnet.numpy.ndarray.

A boolean value indicating whether the NumPy-array semantics should be turned on or off. When this flag is set to True, it enables Gluon code flow to use or generate mxnet.numpy.ndarray`s instead of `mxnet.ndarray.NDArray. For example, a Block would create parameters of type mxnet.numpy.ndarray.
